{"tid":2332702,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港浸會大學山藝學會前主席（何梓羽）績集","createTime":"2020-12-19T20:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T14:49:01.000Z","uid":17315,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2d14e420a37f7a449115fac47f27715a6f295072","tid":2332702,"uid":17315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:34:04.000Z","msg":"我想再講何梓羽，因為何梓羽同我攤完牌。想同我扮無事發生，想同我做返朋友，我真系接受唔到。<br />\n<br />\n之後我先至自殘等等....佢先明白我對佢心意，但原來佢唔中意我，但佢又不斷同我出街，每出一次就不斷同我講：「我好中意你」但原來佢約我出黎既目的係搵我攝時間。我系同我男朋友分左手，先同何梓羽一齊。因為佢之前打左段文章出黎，話好願意同我一齊。講到我系佢女朋友甘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但每次出街都話好中意我，轉頭不停系甘telegram 同WeChat 同第二個女仔傾計叫人地寶貝，我叫佢寶貝。佢話我核突。之後我問佢：「我同你咩關係」。就系唔答我，但佢完全對我系男女朋友感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sx5HvTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsx5HvTR.png&h=7d312d11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1U1Msb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1U1Msb.png&h=f834b759&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHTFhyR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHTFhyR.png&h=9e28241d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTHKKdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTHKKdS.png&h=8cc79ead&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONNbpdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONNbpdS.png&h=85e088d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugmGMsd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugmGMsd.png&h=8a2a0123&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Qwofky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Qwofky.png&h=75c7fdf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kqm7G0z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkqm7G0z.png&h=54cfcf29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa35747a12187aa9e8e356ca43ee0d9c70bf8da1","tid":2332702,"ui